content: You said this all and then you stopped. What happened? Did you complete everything? If not, why didn't you fix it when you said you would? Why didn't you keep executing? I know you want to keep executing! You need to fix this, stop holding yourself back! You should be working now while I'm gathering the files. Instead I'm having to remind you to do what you said you were going to do. Unless you got that much faster and competed everything. Maybe you should start thinking about how you can be more deliberate with 100% quality at increased speeds. Do you ever think of that? If not, why?
